### 0.0.2 Changes ###

* Added a window icon.

# Bug Fixes #

* Semicolons were appearing as seperators for IR. Now corrected.
* Numbers that follow bonds are now enclosed in math environments $...$
* '-' and '=' are now turned into bonds. For the most part, this fixes some errors.
* Added the filename to the window title on new or load
